image.altText: A room with ocean views.

props.synopsis: The prime minister's seaside property purchase raised eyebrows, but many politicians have larger property holdings.

title.children: With the PM's $4.3 million property purchase in the spotlight, the ABC analysed all federal politicians' real estate holdings

image.altText: The exterior of a large house.

props.synopsis: Buying a fancy house when you already have two taxpayer-funded ones to live in plus a fully paid-off investment property, just before an election, in the hot flush of a genuine housing crisis, is kind of bold.

image.altText: A close up photo of a man wearing a suit and blue tie.

image.altText: An older woman with short grey hair and rounded glasses smiles.

image.altText: A graphic hows two men shaking hands with blue shining behind him and red shining behind the other man.

image.altText: Kylian Mbappé stands on the pitch in a Real Madrid jersey with his lips pursed.

image.altText: A woman in a white long-sleeve and collared shirt with shoulder-length black hair sits behind a desk

image.altText: A rendered image of a large two-towered white building surrounded by trees.
